{{GuiCommand/de
|Name=Draft AutoGroup
|Name/de=Draft AutoGruppieren
|Empty=1
|Workbenches=[[Draft_Workbench/de|Draft]], [[BIM_Workbench/de|BIM]]
|Version=0.17
|SeeAlso=[[Draft_Layer/de|Draft Layer]], [[Std_Group/de|Std Gruppe]]
